## 🌠 Giessen joins the Galaxy Training Academy 2025 with on site support 🎉

We are very excited, that the Galaxy Training Academy starts in less than one week. We are happy to anounce that Giessen, Germany, is hosting the first on site location 🚀. They are offering a room for participants during the GTA and office ours to discuss questions with. 

- 📆 **Dates**:  May 12-16, 2025
- 📍 **Location** 🌍:  Global online
- 📍 **First on site location**:  Gissen

If you would like to join the offer in Giessen please contact Jochen to get further information.


If you are not located in Gissen you can join the Galaxy Training Academy online. You will get 24 hours support online. [Register now](https://forms.gle/xqZMd4gduwJ6XyKU6)! 🎉

To learn more about the [program]({% link events/2025-05-12-galaxy-academy-2025.md %}#monday-introduction) and review the event outline, visit the [event page]({% link events/2025-05-12-galaxy-academy-2025.md %}).